quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  4,116,"God forgives not that aught should be with Him associated; less than that He forgives to whomsoever He will. Whoso associates with God anything, has gone astray into far error"
  4,117,"In stead of Him, they pray not except to female beings; they pray not except to a rebel Satan accursed by God"
  4,118,"He said, 'Assuredly I will take unto myself a portion appointed of Thy servants"
  4,119,"and I will lead them astray, and fill them with fancies and I will command them and they will cut off the cattle's ears; I will command them and they will alter God's creation.' Whoso takes Satan to him for a friend, instead of God, has surely suffered a manifest loss"
  4,120,"He promises them and fills them with fancies, but there is nothing Satan promises them except delusion"
  4,121,"Such men -- their refuge shall be Gehenna, and they shall find no asylum from it"
  4,122,"But those that believe, and do deeds of righteousness, them We shall admit to gardens underneath which rivers flow, therein dwelling for ever and ever; God's promise in truth; and who is truer in speech than God"
  4,123,"It is not your fancies, nor the fancies of the People of the Book. Whosoever does evil shall be recompensed for it, and will not find for him, apart from God, a friend or helper"
  4,124,"And whosoever does deeds of righteousness, be it male or female, believing - they shall enter Paradise, and not be wronged a single date-spot"
  4,125,"And who is there that has a fairer religion than he who submits his will to God being a good-doer, and who follows the creed of Abraham, a man of pure faith? And God took Abraham for a friend"
  4,126,"To God belongs all that is in the heavens and in the earth, and God encompasses everything"